{"tid":1675590,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［攻略］唔好以為區選贏硬，仲有好多野要人人都做","createTime":"2019-10-26T04:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T04:42:53.000Z","uid":39021,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0133e63a44c70d1221123b1c439192308766a3","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"區選仍然係重要民意指標，就算你覺得個選舉係廢既<br />\n從經濟考慮上，建制贏得愈少，收少亦都會減少<br />\n雖然民意好硬淨，但唔係贏硬，有幾點要注意<br />\n<br />\n1. 種票、七姓、隱形人<br />\n呢個除咗較查冊之外我地難以有效反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔討論<br />\n<br />\n2. 偽黃假獨立<br />\n好多區巴打努力起緊底，詳細請睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vS3AyME4nRbActwuq8HVkA0SQ81dUEpq8wZLEmKo4dBOKS6_UVDqkO5Llzwqlk9JGWwdQ7OqTZijhNy/pubhtml?fbclid=IwAR2OMJSQdyUnu0M4cVg2Es3MGJjh8eFn6OwI8_VB8tXDGV2JtkDJVHDGI_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2Fe%2F2PACX-1vS3AyME4nRbActwuq8HVkA0SQ81dUEpq8wZLEmKo4dBOKS6_UVDqkO5Llzwqlk9JGWwdQ7OqTZijhNy%2Fpubhtml%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2OMJSQdyUnu0M4cVg2Es3MGJjh8eFn6OwI8_VB8tXDGV2JtkDJVHDGI_A&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=e0d12962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vS3AyME4nRbActwuq8HVkA0SQ81dUEpq8wZLEmKo4dBOKS6_UVDqkO5Llzwqlk9JGWwdQ7OqTZijhNy/pubhtml?fbclid=IwAR2OMJSQdyUnu0M4cVg2Es3MGJjh8eFn6OwI8_VB8tXDGV2JtkDJVHDGI_A</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 自己友打自己友＋含淚投票<br />\nNOW之前都報過，因為Plan B問題，造就大量黃絲候選人同時出選問題<br />\n雖然民意堅實，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">分薄票源係極嚴重既問題，隨時令到藍絲翻生</span></strong><br />\n另外，唔同黃絲候選人可能各自有問題<br />\n最常見係一個候選人hea做，另一個候選人藉藉無名，好似兩個都投唔落咁<br />\n不過區區問題唔同，難以一概而論究竟要投邊一個<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>呼籲大家先行去地區Facebook同TG group搞預選，提早決定押注落邊一個身上！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 票站舞弊<br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得，上年立法會選舉大埔有個站多咗好多票出黎<br />\n到依家都未查到究竟係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以到<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>投票當日時，各位街坊要加緊留意票站附近有無異常<br />\n有異常要立即影相＋Timestamp，每一張相都可以成為重要證據</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n5. 恐嚇<br />\n好多候選人受到恐嚇，何君妖都出動想嚇人退選<br />\n我地好難保護到咁多人，但最少我地可以鼓勵候選人<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>大家喺街上見到受逼迫既候選人，不妨主動上前鼓勵<br />\n每一句鼓勵都會令到候選人更堅定</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b2e4859d99ceed108d808d2cfa66308fe3ca4550","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00eb74b3682c38f5c8227eccef65c0abf364761","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e374654f5b80990f9b061a7431b76522d6fbc1b5","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf2748de2c36ee1cbafd87ca64c6bc6b40acb77","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ea2c3210ada42d7ec1621b3829dd5279a66110","tid":1675590,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"[堅行動post][求三連]三分鐘Twitter 戰線傳送門 10月26號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675453</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54887cf03d3d109ba0af41d7fade8c48cdd5fdc9","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073a1087aaa7f60dcba922f3db3daf560bb10113","tid":1675590,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:24:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1e19cfe40211181b3711df0b0f8100b97e5dcbca","tid":1675590,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78edd84ed9bcbd7d7639a6ff895a67494e25746f","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d175abfd23e2401ef10635578dca5999640d12b","tid":1675590,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}